	psmodules_install on each compute node (copy modules to /lib/modules/...).


Version pscom-4.0.6:
============================

2003-12-15  Jens Hauke  <hauke@par-tec.com>

	* Bugfix: Fix EXPORT_SYMBOL() in all Modules.

2003-11-26  Jens Hauke  <hauke@par-tec.com>

	* Modification: ia64 smp optimization in libpsport4.

	* Modification: Changes for mvapi (infiniband) version
	thca-ia64-3.0.1-2.4.18_e.31smp.

	* Extension: Changes for Opteron (AMD, x86_64).

2003-11-21  Jens Hauke  <hauke@par-tec.com>

	* Extension: Add p4tcp to the distribution.

	* Extension: Register remote connections in accept (bookkeeping of
	all connections). This need a p4sock module with the
	dump_usr_ci(self) extension for p4sock communication!

	* Extension: dump_usr_ci with -1 (self); new function
	p4_shutdown() for psockt and TCP shutdown(); first vision of
	SYNNACK for faster "connection refused";

2003-11-18  Jens Hauke  <hauke@par-tec.com>

	* Extension: p4tcp tool. interface for external configuration of
